      <title>亿万富翁郭台铭的八年股票目标终于实现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/foxconn-billionaire-s-eight-year-stock-target-finally-comes-true</link>
      <description><![CDATA[iPhone 组装商富士康科技集团的亿万富翁创始人郭台铭终于实现了他大约八年来一直未能实现的目标。]]></description>
