    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将根据新职责启动“全面”支付审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/australia-will-launch-holistic-payments-review-under-new-remit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员表示，澳大利亚央行正在与政府合作，对该国零售支付监管框架进行现代化改造，随后将对该行业进行“全面审查”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/australia-will-launch-holistic-payments-review-under-new-remit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 00:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
